---
title: Chipotle Chicken Wings and Crispy Jumbo Shrimp Platter with Potato Wedges and Creamy Coleslaw
description: Chipotle makes everything better — especially succulent chicken wings! This meal is packed with flavour, from the oven-baked wings to the shallow-fried breaded jumbo shrimp. Creamy coleslaw cools everything down.
